sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as GIF System
    participant Database as GIF Database

    User->>System: Search for GIFs
    System->>Database: Query GIFs based on search criteria
    Database-->>System: Return GIF results
    System-->>User: Display GIF results

    User->>System: Select a GIF to send
    System->>Database: Retrieve selected GIF
    Database-->>System: Return selected GIF
    System-->>User: Confirm GIF ready for sending

    User->>System: Send GIF
    System->>Database: Store sent GIF details
    Database-->>System: Confirm storage
    System-->>User: Notify GIF sent successfully